Instead of starting with the Throne Room, it uses Careful Planning to deploy Obi's hut and Lars Farm.
Add Revos, Oola, and several Harvests, and mix well!</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000">Cards</Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Locations (6)<br>
